snippet.title: Yang Jian - Truth Unveiled (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
His third eye can see through all things, but cannot see the answer to true justice.
On the path of righteousness, he has faced many obstacles and almost lost his life.
However, even if there is no justice in this world, he will use his spear to carve out his own path.
He is Yun Chuan, the guardian of justice.
